                            <comment id="183909" author="michael.kuhn" created="Wed, 8 Feb 2017 10:12:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the hint! I have updated the patch accordingly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="183896" author="ake_s" created="Wed, 8 Feb 2017 06:55:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It might be more consistent to do this the same way that posix_acl_from_xattr and posix_acl_to_xattr are handled, in libcfs/include/libcfs/linux/linux-fs.h&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="183825" author="michael.kuhn" created="Tue, 7 Feb 2017 20:53:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;By the way, this also applies to Linux 4.4 on Ubuntu 16.04 because Canonical has decided to backport this change.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
